1. Clone dotfiles: 
git clone https://github.com/wzygzlm/dotfiles.git

2. Install HomeBrew and required package:
brew install tmux mutt offlineimap ncdu ranger cmus vim fonts-powerline msmtp cscope exuberant-ctags

3. Clone powerline-shell: 
cd && git clone https://github.com/b-ryan/powerline-shell.git && git clone https://github.com/erikw/tmux-powerline.git

4. Install the powerline-shell: 
cd powerline-shell && sudo python setup.py install

5. Clone tmux-powerline

6. Install oh-my-zsh

7. Copy all the files from dotfiles/ubuntu to ~/.:
cd && cp -rf dotfiles/ubuntu/.[^.]* ~/ && cp -rf dotfiles/ubuntu/* ~/

8. Clone vim vundle:
git clone https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim
